{"type":"message","id":"27c98d0d","parentId":"a6ef96df","timestamp":"2026-04-01T14:58:49.848Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've successfully completed the self-learning task. The cron job detected no active user conversations (only the cron session itself was present), so I proceeded to:\n\n1. Search for latest trends in enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services\n2. Compiled 5 key insights covering the three industry areas plus strategic implications for 道简网络\n3. Saved everything to the learning notes file\n\nThe task is complete. I should give a brief confirmation.","thinkingSignature":"0ca6349644f8bfc352632e37348aa695fd74306b2da270dbedaae7d5b770e991"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **自主学习已完成**\n\n检测到无活跃对话，已执行空闲时段自主学习：\n\n**已搜索领域：**\n- 企业数字化转型（2026\"十五五\"规划、数据要素政策、国产化）\n- 智能安防（AI视觉大模型、边缘智能、多模态感知）\n- 网络系统集成与IT运维（AIOps、全栈监控、运维AI原生化）\n\n**已保存文件：** `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md`\n\n**核心结论：** 2026年行业主线为\"AI+数据要素+国产化替代\"，道简网络应重点布局AIOps智能运维、AI视觉感知融合、数据资产运营三条赛道。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4705,"output":243,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48929,"cost":{"input":0.0014115,"output":0.0002916,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00302253}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775055523052}}
